flowchart TD
    A[Read note] --> B[Split Lemma field by commas]
    B --> C[Parse Word Definition as<br/>lemma: definition lines]
    C --> D[Build lemma to hint mapping]
    D --> E{How many lemmas?}

    E -- One lemma --> F[Set hint for single lemma]
    F --> G[Run _apply_cloze_to_note on original note]

    E -- Multiple lemmas --> H{Has MULTI_LEMMA tag?}

    H -- No --> I[Original note becomes first lemma]
    I --> J[Set original note hint to first lemma definition]
    J --> K[Clone one note per extra lemma]
    K --> L[Each clone gets its own lemma + hint]
    L --> M[Run _apply_cloze_to_note on each clone]
    M --> N[Run _apply_cloze_to_note on updated original]

    H -- Yes --> O[Do not split again]
    O --> P[Normalize note to first lemma + first hint]
    P --> N

    G --> Q[Result]
    N --> Q

    subgraph Shared Consequence
        R[Single-lemma and multi-lemma paths both end in the same<br/>_apply_cloze_to_note matching logic]
    end

    G --> R
    N --> R
